<div data-bg="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Rachel-Connolly.jpg" class="article-feature-image-full-width-container --slim rocket-lazyload" data-background="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Rachel-Connolly.jpg" style></div> <div class="background-grey --no-padding background-gradient background-box-shadow">
